  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Subjects with type 2 diabetes

          -  Treated by diet for at least 3 months

          -  Never treated with hypoglycaemic drugs

          -  HbA1c (glycaemic haemoglobin A1c) on inclusion time superior to 6.5%

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Very symptomatic diabetes

          -  Advanced vascular complications

          -  Manifest renal failure

          -  Manifest hepatic disease

          -  Pregnancy, breast feeding or intention to become pregnant or if it is considered that
             the patient is not using adequate contraceptive measures. Adequate contraceptive
             measures are considered to be an intrauterine device, oral contraceptives and barrier
             methods
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
